  <trk>
    <name>Chapel path Visperterminen and Bodmeri Suone</name>
    <desc>The inspiring ascent leads along several historic chapels up to the forest chapel above Visperterminen. Afterwards, you hike along the Bodmeri Suone and through the forest back down to Visperterminen.</desc>
